01:00:41.042 --> 01:00:42.000
MALE SPEAKER: One more.

01:00:42.000 --> 01:00:44.130
JULIE JAMES: All
right, one more.

01:00:44.130 --> 01:00:49.450
This is a good one from
JNN 38364 up in Ontario.

01:00:49.450 --> 01:00:52.220
Uncle George, which I
love that she calls you

01:00:52.220 --> 01:00:54.820
that, you have been through
so much in your life,

01:00:54.820 --> 01:00:57.070
was it difficult to play
a role in the production

01:00:57.070 --> 01:01:00.210
without getting overly
emotional, or was the show

01:01:00.210 --> 01:01:04.024
and sharing the story
more therapeutic?

01:01:04.024 --> 01:01:05.940
GEORGE TAKEI: Well, she's
my niece calling in.

01:01:10.730 --> 01:01:12.392
You know, the characters--

01:01:12.392 --> 01:01:14.266
JULIE JAMES: Wait, you
said I was your niece.

01:01:14.266 --> 01:01:16.307
GEORGE TAKEI: I have a
lot of nieces, believe me.

01:01:16.307 --> 01:01:17.690
JULIE JAMES: And nephews.

01:01:17.690 --> 01:01:19.920
GEORGE TAKEI: Blond haired
ones, red haired ones,

01:01:19.920 --> 01:01:20.860
freckled face nieces.

01:01:24.480 --> 01:01:30.890
This play is so specific and,
as was said, so universal.

01:01:30.890 --> 01:01:38.610
The characters are so rich and
so human and to be one of them,

01:01:38.610 --> 01:01:42.510
in this story, it
tears me apart.

01:01:42.510 --> 01:01:48.150
And I am reliving that
and, yes, it's a catharsis.

01:01:48.150 --> 01:01:51.230
I have a final
scene there as Sam

01:01:51.230 --> 01:01:56.660
that is an opportunity
for me to feel everything

01:01:56.660 --> 01:02:01.090
that I've felt as an
adult and let it hang out.

01:02:01.090 --> 01:02:04.410
It's a wonderful, wonderful,
personal as well as

01:02:04.410 --> 01:02:06.257
professional experience.

01:02:06.257 --> 01:02:08.590
JULIE JAMES: And I love that
you said it was your legacy

01:02:08.590 --> 01:02:11.570
and that just is
so, so touching.

01:02:11.570 --> 01:02:15.310
And we cannot wait to get
more news for "Allegiance"

01:02:15.310 --> 01:02:20.910
to come to Broadway,
in your words, 2015.

01:02:20.910 --> 01:02:23.530
Let's put the good joujou
out there everybody.

01:02:23.530 --> 01:02:25.930
